Dialogue: 0,0:00:-12.-27,0:00:-10.-26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-10.-24,0:00:-08.-36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger,\Nthe King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-08.-34,0:00:-06.-05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-06.-03,0:00:-02.-18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before\Nhis death drove people to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-02.-16,0:00:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure?\NIf you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.67,0:00:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.85,0:00:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men head for the\NGrand Line in pursuit of their dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.59,0:00:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly\Nentered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.49,0:00:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.86,0:00:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.77,0:00:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.97,0:00:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.61,0:00:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever,\NI take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it's not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.46,0:01:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.17,0:01:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard\Nsomeone else's biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.47,0:01:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn't there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.14,0:01:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.65,0:01:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.36,0:01:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand do you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.60,0:01:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.97,0:01:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.50,0:01:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami would never kill Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.31,0:01:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.47,0:01:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're friends, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.04,0:01:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.38,0:01:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a pathetic bunch of\Npeople cooperating with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.05,0:01:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.32,0:01:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that'd hit you hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.53,0:02:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that someone\Nreally showed up for her...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.93,0:02:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.17,0:02:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The most painful word for her...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.51,0:02:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's how Nami pretended\Nto kill me and let me escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.48,0:02:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks to me like there's a reason\Nshe's in a fishman pirate group!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.95,0:02:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, don't get any more\Ninvolved with this village.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.49,0:02:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave Nami alone.\NI'll explain the circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.89,0:02:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'll pass.\N--H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.10,0:02:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about her past.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.83,0:02:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Where are you going, Luffy?!\N--For a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.43,0:02:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's he?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.14,0:02:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Untold Past! Female Warrior Bellemere!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.21,0:02:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.05,0:03:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we really did see a\Nship fall from the sky, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.99,0:03:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems some unordinary humans\Nhave stepped foot on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.76,0:03:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who could it be? And why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.93,0:03:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! Who's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.00,0:03:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not from this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.61,0:03:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? So those are fishmen?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.40,0:03:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! Wait! You!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.97,0:03:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You called?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.64,0:03:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.31,0:03:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing on this island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.18,0:04:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does it matter to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.28,0:04:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah. You have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.38,0:04:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Luffy. I'm taking a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.15,0:04:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A walk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.39,0:04:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.86,0:04:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You! Where are you headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.83,0:04:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heck if I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.33,0:04:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He seems like a funny guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.77,0:04:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.11,0:04:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He walked right by us,\Nwith no fear whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.27,0:04:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a mysterious guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.35,0:04:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellemere?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.75,0:04:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this person raised you and Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.62,0:04:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.69,0:04:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I start to explain\Nabout Bellemere-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.50,0:04:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I fell asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.24,0:05:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Nojiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.21,0:05:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where could she have gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.15,0:05:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little more, Bellemere-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little more,\Nand everything will return!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.19,0:05:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cocoyashi Village,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.16,0:05:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the tangerine orchard,\Nand even my dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.43,0:05:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It took eight years...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.01,0:05:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All done...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.31,0:05:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All done!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.19,0:06:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I just need to check that book...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Nacchan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.74,0:06:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.24,0:06:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing! Nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.83,0:06:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.33,0:06:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, Nami! Not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.93,0:06:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh? Did it again, Nacchan?\N--Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.03,0:06:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You just never learn!\N--I'm not a cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.11,0:06:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times do I have to\Ntell you stealing is wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.47,0:06:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bleh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.61,0:06:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not my fault we're poor!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.55,0:06:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheapskate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.25,0:06:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellemere!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.22,0:06:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellemere! Your no-good\Ncat's been at it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.73,0:07:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whadya want? You're annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.56,0:07:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Welcome home, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.80,0:07:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.33,0:07:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! This is the umpteenth time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.80,0:07:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's even famous in the village now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.64,0:07:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.71,0:07:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely even you've\Nshoplifted before, Gen-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.98,0:07:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why she acts this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.21,0:07:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.85,0:07:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Alright. You paid for her, right?\N--B-Bellemere...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.29,0:07:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks so much.\NI don't have money right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.22,0:07:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pay you later...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.42,0:07:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...with my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.99,0:07:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't be s-saying\Nthings like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.77,0:07:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at you blush!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.91,0:07:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? And why are you laughing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.28,0:07:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try that again and\Nyou'll get 100 spankings!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.68,0:07:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.42,0:08:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I really wanted this book!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.89,0:08:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanted it,\Nwhy didn't you just tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.39,0:08:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you wouldn't\Nbuy it for me anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.49,0:08:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I would!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.99,0:08:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We do have some\Nmoney stashed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.23,0:08:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the villagers said the\Nclimate's been so good lately
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.07,0:08:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that you can get tons of\Ntangerines from any old field,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.97,0:08:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and our tangerines won't sell good\N'cause they don't go up in value.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.27,0:08:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can mind their own business!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.58,0:08:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so dumb, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.74,0:08:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would've stolen it way better!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.75,0:08:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said no stealing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.42,0:08:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.92,0:08:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.09,0:08:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know,\Nthere's one thing for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.93,0:08:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The maps you draw are\Nreally amazing, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First you learned how to draw\Nsea charts, and now land maps!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.57,0:08:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a map of this island, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.21,0:09:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one would ever think\Nsuch a little kid drew this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.81,0:09:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm studying navigation too now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.45,0:09:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Navigation, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.49,0:09:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is Nami's dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.55,0:09:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.82,0:09:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna use my navigation skills\Nto travel to all the world's oceans!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.43,0:09:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then I'm gonna make a\Nworld map of everything I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.37,0:09:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So your map of this island is your\Nfirst step toward your dream, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.70,0:09:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.47,0:09:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A map of the world, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.88,0:09:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami! Someday, you will\Nmake your dream come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.08,0:09:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.89,0:09:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Bellemere-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.29,0:09:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't been eating meals lately...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.83,0:09:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been eating tangerines,\Nthough. I'm on a diet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.03,0:09:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need any meals, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.07,0:09:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you taking interest in guys for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.94,0:09:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kids need to eat right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.10,0:10:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You keep lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.61,0:10:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have any food because\Nwe don't have any money!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.68,0:10:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For reals?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.81,0:10:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You're suffering, so that we can...\N--Diet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.85,0:10:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't underestimate\Nthe beautifying power of tangerines!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.85,0:10:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're the reason I still have\Nsuch lustrous skin at the age of 30!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.49,0:10:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But your hands are yellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.36,0:10:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just shut up and eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.06,0:10:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are, Nami! All done!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.13,0:10:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A super custom-made\NBellemere brand!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.90,0:10:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another hand-me-down from Nojiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.77,0:10:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!\NIt looks great on you, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.61,0:10:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This lion used to be a sunflower!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.61,0:10:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.48,0:10:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're two years younger\Nthan me, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.38,0:10:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Age has nothing to do with it!\NI want new clothes too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.48,0:10:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine are old clothes too, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.62,0:10:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You get my stuff 'cause\Nyou're my baby sister! Blehh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.62,0:10:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not your real sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.09,0:10:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not related by blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.23,0:11:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.67,0:11:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellemere-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.11,0:11:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what if you're not\Nrelated by blood?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.69,0:11:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never say anything\Nstupid like that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Whatever...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.13,0:11:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not our real mother, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.30,0:11:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd be better off\Nwithout us, wouldn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.20,0:11:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That way, you could eat,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.77,0:11:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,buy all the clothes\Nyou want, and be free!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.67,0:11:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.48,0:11:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish someone richer\Nhad adopted me instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.32,0:11:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.32,0:12:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, then! Do whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.43,0:12:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hate this house that much,\Nthen go leave for somewhere else!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.43,0:12:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.10,0:12:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.87,0:12:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.24,0:12:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.57,0:12:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellemere-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.44,0:12:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The three of us are a family!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.04,0:12:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Nami feels the same way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.84,0:13:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't mean what she said!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.02,0:13:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a strong person, Nojiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.42,0:13:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was real immature of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.63,0:13:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you go bring Nami back for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.73,0:13:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have a super delicious\Nsupper ready before you get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.73,0:13:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.45,0:13:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Miss! I'll lower it to this much!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.55,0:13:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Lower it a little more!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.12,0:13:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right over here!\NLow prices! Low prices!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.89,0:13:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't hurt to buy any of\Nthese fresh fruits lined up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.07,0:13:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, coming here from the outskirts\Nof the village is "running away"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.24,0:13:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's sure nice and convenient!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.41,0:14:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Drink up before it gets cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.41,0:14:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellemere-san would be\Nhappier if we were gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.88,0:14:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.19,0:14:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having two children\Ncosts lots of money...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.22,0:14:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And everyone in the village\Nhates her, because of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.33,0:14:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're old enough to\Nconsider others now, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.93,0:14:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.17,0:14:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was a famous brat in this\Nvillage when she was your age, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.47,0:14:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellemere-san was?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.14,0:14:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, she's still quite\Na brat in the villagers' eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.51,0:14:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How shocked the village was\Nwhen that brat suddenly said
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.28,0:14:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she was going to be a marine...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.91,0:14:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A marine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.92,0:14:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellemere-san was a marine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.62,0:14:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.16,0:14:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates have to pay for\Nslaughtering innocent people...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:15:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With those words, she left the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.84,0:15:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She says she felt her time\Nto die had finally come...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.08,0:15:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.87,0:15:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your baby sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.11,0:15:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I don't know who she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.52,0:15:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no idea\Nhow that makes me feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.57,0:16:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that was you, Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.31,0:16:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When she saw you, Bellemere\Nmustered up the will to live again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.72,0:16:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a boat! I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.99,0:16:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On a stormy night like tonight?!\NWho on earth could it be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.94,0:16:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor! Call the doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.31,0:16:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellemere? Is that you, Bellemere?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.14,0:16:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Bellemere!\N--What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.05,0:16:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Who are these children?!\N--Doctor! They have terrible fevers!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.09,0:16:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've been completely\Nworn out by the storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.56,0:17:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.76,0:17:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! But we need to tend to\Nthose nasty wounds of yours, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.70,0:17:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.63,0:17:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Don't let them die!\NSave those kids' lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.37,0:17:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I beg of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.91,0:17:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just say, girl ruffian?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.75,0:17:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be these kids' parent.\NThat's what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.45,0:17:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.58,0:17:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it! A punk like you\Ncan't possibly raise children!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.09,0:17:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Take my advice! Give them\Nto a government institution!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.83,0:17:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.33,0:17:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an adult now, too.\NI was even in the navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.33,0:17:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm a little\Nmore upstanding now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.87,0:17:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to take the responsibility\Nof raising these kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.81,0:17:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to raise them\Nto be wonderful people
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.94,0:17:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who won't lose to the era we live in!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.21,0:17:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to live with these kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.65,0:18:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami and Nojiko gave me life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.09,0:18:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You girls have a bond that goes\Nfar deeper than a real family's.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.90,0:18:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami! I thought you'd be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.30,0:18:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nojiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.30,0:18:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellemere-san is waiting for us!\NShe's making a yummy supper!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.74,0:18:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.48,0:18:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet it's your favorite!\NOmelets with tangerine sauce!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.08,0:18:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.42,0:18:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! Omelets!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.16,0:18:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How time flies...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.12,0:18:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Children once on the brink\Nof death, now so full of life...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.53,0:18:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watching them grow up\Nis like a joy for all of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.77,0:18:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! We won't feel happy until\Nwe see that family of three happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.27,0:18:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.71,0:19:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.05,0:19:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.05,0:19:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates are coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.25,0:19:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates! Everyone hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.57,0:19:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's the Arlong Pirates!\N--Arlong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.57,0:19:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.07,0:19:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are fishmen from\Nthe Grand Line doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.91,0:19:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was the rumor about a split in\Nthe fishman pirate group true?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.51,0:19:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami! Nojiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.15,0:19:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.75,0:19:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous here!\NHide in the back woods!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.32,0:19:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.52,0:19:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.23,0:19:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be in excellent\Nspirits, pathetic humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.87,0:19:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As of this moment, this village--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.00,0:20:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no, this island is now\Nunder my control!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.18,0:20:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.78,0:20:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On this memorable day, you will\Nall buy your lives from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.52,0:20:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,100,000 Berries per adult.\N50,000 Berries per kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.09,0:20:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who can't pay... die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.46,0:20:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do, Nojiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.43,0:20:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't pay that much!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.63,0:20:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they might not spot our house!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.73,0:20:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't see it from the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.81,0:20:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much did we get, brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.48,0:20:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just over 25 million, I'd say.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.48,0:20:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.09,0:20:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like we'll hafta pay\Nfor our lives every month
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.99,0:20:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at 100,000 Berries\Nper person from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.43,0:20:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,100,000?! We can't\Nmake a living that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.89,0:20:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Endure it for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.10,0:21:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should just be glad no\None in the village has died.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.67,0:21:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If money is all that's needed,\Nit's an easy price to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.84,0:21:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I at least hope they'll leave\Nwithout noticing Bellemere's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.08,0:21:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the two children, it would\Ncome to 200,000 Berries...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.45,0:21:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt she has that much saved up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.62,0:21:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Time to go, brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.76,0:21:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arlong-san! There's smoke\Ncoming from outside the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.20,0:21:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.50,0:21:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's see!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.30,0:21:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.91,0:21:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing's quite like Bellemere's\NSpecial Tangerine Sauce!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.47,0:21:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami and Nojiko are gonna\Nleap out of their seats!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.28,0:21:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The smoke is coming from a house!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.38,0:21:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? We almost missed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.18,0:21:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.65,0:21:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellemere-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.09,0:22:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go! Let's collect our money!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.76,0:22:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, this is bad! The pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.49,0:22:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...are headed to Bellemere's house!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.60,0:22:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Nojiko and Nami are gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.10,0:22:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.44,0:22:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten more minutes for the duck in\Nthe oven. And the stew is boiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.48,0:22:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This'll be a big blow\Nto our family budget.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.51,0:22:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess I'll splurge, anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.45,0:22:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellemere-san's gonna...\NBellemere-san's gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.76,0:22:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellemere-san's gonna be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.07,0:22:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My overflowing feelings don't connect
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.07,0:22:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as I firmly squeeze your hand back
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.98,0:22:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll set off by myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.91,0:23:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so keep watching me intently\Nas I go into the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.76,0:23:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking about it\Na bit since this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.76,0:23:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it so hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.33,0:23:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting from some point, I haven't\Nbeen able to get away from that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.81,0:23:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to catch those\Nfeelings that rushed off,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.68,0:23:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm already about\Nto overtake myself, even
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.56,0:23:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to embrace my\Ndreams that have jumped out
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.56,0:23:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With you, I can run there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.51,0:23:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! How cute Nami-san\Nwas as a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.41,0:24:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, were you even\Nlistening to the story?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.68,0:24:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I was!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.81,0:24:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd listen to every single\Nword that's about Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.05,0:24:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Got that?!\N--Yes, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.72,0:24:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, why am I apologizing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.15,0:24:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it over? Where's Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.52,0:24:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was really sleeping?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.99,0:24:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.33,0:24:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Survive! Mother Bellemere\Nand Nami's Bond!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.26,0:24:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
